	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Option 3, &amp;quot;Repeat,&amp;quot; means to say or do something again, which is not what is being requested here.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Option 4, &amp;quot;None of these,&amp;quot; is incorrect because &amp;quot;Refer&amp;quot; is the appropriate word for this context.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Therefore, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;Option 2&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

