questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this section, each item consists of six sentences of a passage. The first and sixth sentences are given as S1 and S6. The middle four sentences in each have been jumbled up and labeled as P, Q, R, and S. You are required to find the proper sequence of the four sentences and mark your response accordingly on the Answer Sheet.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;S1: In India, we place too much emphasis on what is often just a piece of paper, instead of the knowledge or skills one should acquire to earn it.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;P: There are numerous careers and fields of work that require advanced knowledge and skill training.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Q: In other words, every person with skills may not receive a degree.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;R: If a student is looking for higher education, a degree is the normal study route.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;S: However, all students may not, and sometimes cannot, take advanced courses and prefer to develop skills that do not necessarily require the rigour of a degree curriculum.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;S6: Similarly, there are many graduates who have theoretical knowledge but no practical experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;div class=&quot;tw-ta-container F0azHf tw-nfl&quot; id=&quot;tw-target-text-container&quot; style=&quot;color: #252525;&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;tw-ta-container F0azHf tw-nfl&quot; id=&quot;tw-target-text-container&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;RPSQ&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Option &amp;lsquo;1&amp;rsquo; is the correct answer. While arranging the parts of the sentence given in the options, we have to find some contextual and grammatical relationships between them. So, let&amp;#39;s find out these connections.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The passage starts by telling us that &amp;lsquo;In India, we tend to place more value on a piece of paper that is often meaningless than on the &lt;strong&gt;knowledge&lt;/strong&gt; or abilities necessary to earn it.&amp;quot; &lt;strong&gt;(S1)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Statement &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;R&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; because it connects the statement &amp;quot;S1&amp;quot; further. It is mentioned here that a &lt;strong&gt;degree &lt;/strong&gt;is the typical path of study for those seeking higher education.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Statement &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;P&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; because it further connects the statement &amp;lsquo;R&amp;rsquo;. There are many professions and fields that &lt;strong&gt;demand higher knowledge&lt;/strong&gt; and skill training than just a paper &lt;strong&gt;degree.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Statement &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;S&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; follows &amp;lsquo;R&amp;rsquo; because it further adds more details about statement P. Not all students are able to take advanced courses, and sometimes they cannot. Instead, some choose to focus on &lt;strong&gt;developing abilities&lt;/strong&gt; that do not necessarily require the rigour of &lt;strong&gt;a degree programme.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Statement &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Q&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; because it further connects the statement &amp;lsquo;S&amp;rsquo;. To put it another way, not everyone with &lt;strong&gt;skills will get a degree.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;lsquo;S6&amp;rsquo;&lt;/strong&gt; is the concluding statement, which states that there are many graduates who have theoretical knowledge but no practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hence, the sequence of the statements will be&lt;/strong&gt;: S1RPSQS6&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Correct Sentence:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;list-style-type: disc;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S1:&lt;/strong&gt; In India, we place too much emphasis on what is often just a piece of paper, instead of the knowledge or skills one should acquire to earn it.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;R:&lt;/strong&gt; If a student is looking for higher education, a degree is the normal study route.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;P:&lt;/strong&gt; There are numerous careers and fields of work that require advanced knowledge and skill training.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S:&lt;/strong&gt; However, all students may not, and sometimes cannot, take advanced courses and prefer to develop skills that do not necessarily require the rigour of a degree curriculum.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Q:&lt;/strong&gt; In other words, every person with skills may not receive a degree.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S6:&lt;/strong&gt; Similarly, there are many graduates who have theoretical knowledge but no practical experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

questions.statement:
&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Directions:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Sentences of a paragraph are given below in jumbled order. Arrange the sentences in the correct order to form a meaningful and coherent paragraph.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;A.&amp;nbsp;At least 25 people were killed over the weekend as torrential rains triggered flash floods and landslips in Himachal Pradesh and Uttarakhand.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;B.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Monsoon rainfall over India is 8% more than what is usual for this time of the year.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;C.&amp;nbsp;Several arterial roads were blocked by debris, as currents washed away bridges and vehicles.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;D.&amp;nbsp;While this might bode well for agriculture in some regions, it also means floods and concentrated downpours with devastating consequences.&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;B,D,A,C.&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Let&amp;#39;s look at the sequence of the sentence.&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;​&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;​Statement B&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is the opening of the sentence as it introduces the subject and the theme of the passage&amp;nbsp;which is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Monsoon rainfall&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;which is 8% more than usual for this time&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;​Statement D &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;the second statement of the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;as it further elaborates the sentence in &lt;strong&gt;B &lt;/strong&gt;by telling us that &lt;strong&gt;monsoon might be well for agriculture in some reason and also means consequences of floods and downpours.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Statement A&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the third&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;statement&amp;nbsp;of the&amp;nbsp;sentence as it tells us &lt;strong&gt;the consequences of monsoon&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;in which&amp;nbsp;at least 25 people were killed over the weekend in&amp;nbsp;Himachal Pradesh and Uttarakhand.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Statement C&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;is the last statement of the sentence and it adds further &lt;strong&gt;the consequences of monsoon that the road were blocked&amp;nbsp;by debris because currents washed away bridges and vehicles.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct sequence is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;B,D,A,C&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Correct&amp;nbsp;Order&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Monsoon rainfall over India is 8% more than what is usual for this time of the year.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;D.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;While this might bode well for agriculture in some regions, it also means floods and concentrated downpours with devastating consequences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;At least 25 people were killed over the weekend as torrential rains triggered flash floods and landslips in Himachal Pradesh and Uttarakhand.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Several arterial roads were blocked by debris, as currents washed away bridges and vehicles.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
